description: The objective of the S&P 500 THEAM EASY UCITS ETF subfund (the Subfund) is to replicate the performance of the S&P 500 index, regardless of its trends. As the Subfund is indexed, it seeks to maintain the tracking err in absolute terms between the growth of the Subfunds net asset value and that of the index at a level below 1%.
name: EasyETF - BNP Paribas Easy S&P 500 UCITS ETF
